column4: Hello, on 6.06 LTS, I just did modprobe zd1211, and I see no eth1 in iwconfig. But if I do the same thing on my desktop (Edgy) with the same USB WiFi adapter, I do see eth1 in iwconfig... what can I do ?
thazt the module is in your Edgy kernel but not in Dapper
it's zd1211rw in Edgy and zd1211 in Dapper
